Just some of my bash settings, so that I can remember.

Ubuntu note:
  - need to install https://bitbucket.org/sjl/hg-prompt
  - need to install vim-nox for vim with ruby support
  - need to install ruby1.8-dev
  - git config --global color.ui true
  - git config --global alias.ci "commit"
  - git config --global alias.co "checkout"
